name: Bockus Ramblings
tagline: A place to host talks that I've given.
body:
### Welcome!
I'm going to use this site as a place to host talks given at user groups, conferences, or to myself (I get lonely sometimes).

### Talks

***

#### Samsung Gear development with the Tizen SDK
This is a lightning talk I gave at the OKC.js user group. Check out the slide deck [here](gear-dev).
